        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩若能如是供養如來，如理相應者，即得無邊世界諸佛菩薩共所稱讚，亦得世間天、人、阿修羅等利養供給，成熟無量無邊眾生，嚴淨佛土，疾成阿耨多羅三藐三菩提果。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a09_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於色法中，能與布施波羅蜜多如理相應者，若修有相施，亦速圓滿布施波羅蜜多；",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a11_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若修無相施，亦速圓滿布施波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a12_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a12_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何是菩薩摩訶薩於色法中，修有相施或無相施？",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a13_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a13_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩於色法中修行布施求解脫時，有所解脫布施可得，有能解脫布施可得，如是修者，當知是菩薩摩訶薩於色法中修有相施。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩於色法中，修行布施求解脫時，無所解脫布施可得，無能解脫布施可得。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a19_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂色自性無所得故，本性無所得故；",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀諸如來亦無所得，本性無所得故。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0862a20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
