        "source_sentence": "故能安住心一境性，此即是為色中無相三摩地。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a15_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a16_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩若於色中，如是如實了知無相三摩地已，受、想、行、識亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a17_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於色法中，應當了知無願三摩地。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a19_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a19_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何是色中無願三摩地？",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩謂於色中得空、無相三摩地已，即於色中觀無性相，而不隨逐所緣行相，有性相亦然，而不隨逐所緣行相，有性無性相亦然，而不隨逐所緣行相，故能安住心一境性，此即是為色中無願三摩地。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a24_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a24_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩若於色中，如是如實了知無願三摩地已，受、想、行、識亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a26_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a27_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於色法中，應當了知有三種義諸行無常。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a28_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為三？",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a28_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、不實義，二、破壞義，三、有垢無垢義。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a29_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864a29_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是，菩薩摩訶薩應當了知有三種義諸行無常。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於色法中，應當了知有三種義諸行是苦。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為三？",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b04_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、無取著義，二、三種相義，三、相續義。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b05_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b05_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是，菩薩摩訶薩應當了知有三種義諸行是苦。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於色法中，應當了知有三種義諸法無我。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為三？",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b09_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、無性無我義，二、有性無性無我義，三、本性清淨無我義。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b11_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是，菩薩摩訶薩應當了知有三種義諸法無我。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b12_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b13_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於色法中，應當了知有三種義涅槃寂靜。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b14_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為三。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b14_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、色中無性畢竟寂靜義，二、有性無性寂靜義，三、本性清淨寂靜義。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b16_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是，菩薩摩訶薩應當了知有三種義涅槃寂靜。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛說此經已，諸菩薩摩訶薩，尊者須菩提，及諸苾芻、苾芻尼、優婆塞、優婆夷，一切世間天、人、阿修羅、乾闥婆等，聞佛所說，皆大歡喜，信受奉行。",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說開覺自性般若波羅蜜多經卷第四",
        "from": "T08n0260_004:0864b22_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]